     PROJECT README

  Project Title
SQL Business Analysis — Orders Data Project
  
  Overview
This project analyzes an e-commerce orders dataset using SQL. The goal is to simulate real business analytics tasks performed by data analysts and BI professionals.
The project covers:
Data cleaning,Date analysis,Window functions,Subqueries,
CTE,Views,Business KPIs and Dataset

  Table: orders_manual
Contains:
Customer details
Product info
Sales amount
Discounts
Order & shipping dates
Payment methods

    Objectives
Clean messy customer data
Analyze sales trends
Measure delivery performance
Identify high-value customers
Perform advanced SQL analytics

   Skills Demonstrated
PostgreSQL querying
Analytical thinking
BI-style problem solving
Query optimization concepts
Window function usage